    "[11] Emergency 2 95.3 Ghosh et al. [12] Disaster Multi 84.0 Our Work Disaster 9 83.76 D. Error Analysis and Cross-Modal BenefitsFigure 6 demonstrates consistent superiority of multimodal fusion across all disaster classes.",
